{"tid":483652,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[淘寶] 為左十蚊 我想請問 有咩方法可以煩到個賣家一頭煙 ?","createTime":"2017-11-29T10:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T15:58:33.000Z","uid":100365,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4ade796ec285ce311b08b3b88a398306771ee984","tid":483652,"uid":100365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:18:15.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n我淘寶買左一包 高達模型 零件<br />\n<br />\n間店叫 <strong>模型超市</strong><br />\n<br />\n係一個指甲鋏咁大既 &quot; 槍 模型  &quot; <br />\n<br />\n大家要明白 , 中國大陸呢D咁開放文明先進同自由既國家<br />\n你要 寄一枝 &quot; 槍 &quot; , 結果就會咁 :<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/181159_ddf5173616641a4749722e8e61770ae4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F181159_ddf5173616641a4749722e8e61770ae4.png&h=7a2bffd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿里旺旺佢個客服<br />\n佢先話 自己咩都唔知 , 肯定係 <strong>你的快遞出了問題</strong><br />\n<br />\n攪左我半日 , 打去圓通問 , 打去順豐問 <br />\n結果係有個 白痴 包裝盒張單度寫左 <strong>槍</strong><br />\n順豐倉拒收 <br />\n<br />\n賣家堅稱自己咩都無寫 ( 點可能咩都唔寫 ? 內容物一定要填 )<br />\n唔係佢錯 , 退款 唔包退 果十蚊運費<br />\n<br />\n我已經 Click 左 <strong>叫淘寶介入</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想問 , 為左呢十蚊 , 我可以點樣煩撚死佢 ?<br />\n因為我返工真係好得閒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\np.s<br />\n我同佢阿里旺旺時係度互串<br />\n大陸客服來說 佢幾有性格  <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"800a23661b21ff7b499387ac6fa89d5804e61d85","tid":483652,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:20:42.000Z","msg":"正常拒簽可以claim運費險，根本唔需要你俾任何運費。"},{"pid":"0fd283a1404d03fd6ed4f792f73690c164b48587","tid":483652,"uid":100365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:21:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常拒簽可以claim運費險，根本唔需要你俾任何運費。</blockquote><br />\n即係其實佢玩野 ?"},{"pid":"5fdf67bdd4f4ad74072b08cd0b7e203832af700b","tid":483652,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:22:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><bloc